{{Quote|This is docking bay 32, isn't it? Yes, it is, and that's what I have here on the requisition form. Everything seems to be in order.|[[Jor Ul Kurax]], to [[Revan/Legends|Revan]]|<ref name="Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref>}}
'''Docking Bay 32''' was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] harbor at [[Anchorhead/Legends|Anchorhead]], [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. [[Revan/Legends|Revan]] used it when visiting the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] on his search for a [[Star Map]] located on Tatooine. [[Jor Ul Kurax]] and [[Mic'tunan'jus Orgu]] both worked in the docking bay at the time of the [[Jedi Civil War]].

